# {{project_name}}

Auto-update endpoint for desktop apps. Returns the latest version + download URL, or 204 if the client is already up to date.

## Bump version

Edit `wrangler.toml` `[vars]`:

```toml
[vars]
CURRENT_VERSION = "0.2.0"
DOWNLOAD_URL_WIN = "https://example.com/myapp-0.2.0-x64.msi"
```

Redeploy. Next launch, every client sees the new version.

## Tauri wiring

In your app's `tauri.conf.json`:
```json
"updater": {
  "active": true,
  "endpoints": ["https://YOUR-WORKER-URL/{{target}}/{{current_version}}"]
}
```
